            <li>Click the topic item that you want to move.</li>
            <li>In the local toolbar click <img src="../../../Images/Shared/move_item_up_btn.png" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> to move the item up or <img src="../../../Images/Shared/move_item_down_btn.png" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> to move the item down.</li>
